OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FNHS maternity services are failing
OL,7,Fwomen, through a raft of problems
OL,8,Franging from a reluctance to admit
OL,9,Fmistakes, racism, staff shortages, and
OL,10,F"a lack of kindness and compassion,"
OL,11,Faccording to a government-ordered
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FAn interim report published by
OL,15,FBaroness Amos as part of her National
OL,16,FMaternity and Neonatal Investigation
OL,17,Ffound deep-rooted issues across the
OL,18,FNHS and a system that "is not working
OL,19,Ffor women, babies and families, or for
OL,20,Fstaff".
OL,26,@zD@WOU|D@FO]
