CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FStories her team heard included a
OL,7,Fdelivery where the delivery room was
OL,8,Ftoo small so a "door had to be left
OL,9,Fopen to provide enough space ` with a
OL,10,Fscreen placed outside of the room to
OL,11,Fprotect families' privacy."
OL,13,FIt added: "It is inconceivable that
OL,14,Fanyone would choose to give birth in
OL,15,Fsuch a manner. We have to ask
OL,16,Fourselves how this can be regarded as
OL,17,Facceptable in 2026?"
OL,26,@yD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
