FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FRacism was also often reported to
OL,7,Finvestigators, including black woman
OL,8,Fsaying they had been told they had
OL,9,F"'tough skin' and able to tolerate
OL,10,Fpain."
OL,12,FThe team also heard that families were
OL,13,Foften not given information about
OL,14,Fwhether their baby had been born alive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
