PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FThis "created distress and long-
OL,7,Flasting trauma for families as they
OL,8,Fstruggled to deal with the fact they
OL,9,Fwere given no clear explanation for
OL,10,Fthe death of their baby, precisely
OL,11,Fbecause their baby was deemed to be
OL,12,Fstillborn."
OL,14,FIn her interim report, Baroness Amos
OL,15,Fsaid "time and time again" families
OL,16,Fand staff see the same issues repeated
OL,17,Fand numerous reviews making
OL,18,Frecommendations. "This cycle must
OL,19,Fstop," she said.
OL,26,@wD@FOUwD@ZO]zD@ROU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
