PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FShe pointed to six factors
OL,7,Fcontributing to pressures on the
OL,8,Fmaternity system, including shortages
OL,9,Fof staff, capacity issues, culture and
OL,10,Fleadership, racism and discrimination,
OL,11,Flack of accountability when things go
OL,12,Fwrong and the poor condition of NHS
OL,13,Fhospitals and buildings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
