PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FShe said: "We have heard about
OL,7,Ffamilies being disregarded and not
OL,8,Flistened to during pregnancy and
OL,9,Flabour, a lack of kindness and
OL,10,Fcompassion, and reluctance on the part
OL,11,Fof trusts and professionals to admit
OL,12,Fmistakes and say sorry when things
OL,13,Fhave gone wrong.
OL,15,FThe investigation also found women
OL,16,Fpointing to a "postcode lottery" of
OL,17,Fcare, with Baroness Amos agreeing
OL,18,F"this looks like a fragmented service".
OL,20,FWhat else did the report find?
OL,26,@nD@KOUxD@OOUxD@`O]zD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
