PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772110991
OL,3,CNHS maternity care 'failing women and
OL,4,Cbabies', investigation finds
OL,6,FBaroness Amos said of her interim
OL,7,Freport: "It is clear from the meetings
OL,8,Fand conversations I have had with
OL,9,Fhundreds of women, families and staff
OL,10,Fmembers across the country, that
OL,11,Fmaternity and neonatal services in
OL,12,FEngland are failing too many women,
OL,13,Fbabies, families and staff."
OL,15,FThe public call for evidence remains
OL,16,Fopen until March 17.
OL,18,FBaroness Amos's final recommendations
OL,19,Fto the NHS in England will be
OL,20,Fpublished in the spring.
